originalText.text: Highly dissatisfactory experience. The receptionist was distasteful, bordering on rude and she spoke so loudly that the entire office could hear your personal details. The “medical” facial was below average, especially given the elevated price point. Not certain what qualifies it as a medical facial - it was essentially a wash, some poorly executed extractions and mask with some product. No frills but will run you $300 easy. Would strongly recommend another, more professional location.
